data.description: Downtown living at it's finest! Charming 3 bed, 2 full bath home. Large living room with wood burning fireplace! The kitchen has gorgeous cork flooring and a gas range; oak & pine flooring throughout rest of home. Large dining area with several windows to let in tons of natural light! 3 hallway closets with lots of storage space. Front load W/D included. Stunning backyard with Large outdoor grilling area with cobblestone pavers. Custom built log cabin tree house in back yard with decks that overlook neighborhood with full bath AC, Wi-Fi, and cable (see write up for additional details). This gem is located in a quiet neighborhood, just 10 blocks from downtown Southern Pines.Pagoda-style chicken coop as well! This home really has it all!
data.whatILove: The backyard with treehouse for studio, guests, or just to enjoy! Rental potential as it has a full bath and queen size loft.
